data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Seller will contribute $10,000.00  towards buyer's closing cost!  Absolutely Gorgeous 5 bedroom, 3 bath home built in 2022.  The house offers many upgrades, from majestic high ceilings and tall doors to ceramic tiles throughout the living areas.   The elegant Kitchen displays Quartz countertops, a beautiful decorative backsplash, 42" cabinets, a large pantry closet, stainless steel appliances, an ample island, recessed and pendant lighting.  The first floor offers an exceptional layout for a two story home, featuring a flex room which is great for an office or den which can be easily converted into a 6th bedroom.  The 5th bedroom and full bath is conveniently located on the first floor which can be used as an in-law suite.  The luxurious iron bar stair railing transfers you to the 2nd floor where you're welcomed by a huge Loft, ideal for a movie theater or game-room.  The Master Suite is followed by the upgraded master bath including dual Quartz countertops, a glass enclosed shower, a rain shower feature and an ample walk-in-closet.  The second bathroom offers dual sinks with a separate shower room and linen closet.  The exterior of the home includes many other upgrades including a water softener, a paved driveway, the privacy of the corner lot with a great curb appeal displaying stone elevation.   The oversized lot offers plenty of space to build your own private pool.  The covered Lanai is great for any outdoor activity.  Enjoy the community amenities with friends and family at the resort style pool or the soccer fields and playground.  Easy access to 417 and 192.
